title: Ep. 156 S&A Investor - Why Obama Is Good For Stocks
itunes:title: Why Obama Is Good For Stocks
description: Todd Schoenberger, Managing Principal at The BlackBay Group, explains why president Obama's win is good news for stocks in 2013. Todd also shares his favorite long and short ideas over the next six months.
